{"tid":1156191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港澳辦：修訂《逃犯條例》必要　須尊重國家的「一制」","createTime":"2019-05-15T12:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T04:02:46.000Z","uid":36134,"like":36,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b96a69b919f795625af16e0035addef6791d5e3e","tid":1156191,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:34:56.000Z","msg":"港澳辦主任張曉明與民主思路訪京團見面時，主動談及修訂《逃犯條例》。港澳辦發布的新聞稿表示，張曉明認為修例工作是必要，又認為要處理目前存在的爭議問題，關鍵是把握好三點，包括要守護法治和公義；要回歸理性和專業；要尊重事實和「一國兩制」下國家的「一制」。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊在會面後有引述張曉明表示，修例是「合適、合理、合法」，香港人不用太擔憂，立法有迫切性，但無提一定要完成立法和立法時限。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家真係扮都唔扮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n差在直接講埋一國一制"},{"pid":"dc105ff44e92857d0d89dd4964c0249feaa629d6","tid":1156191,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:35:18.000Z","msg":"港澳辦：修訂《逃犯條例》必要　須尊重國家的「一制」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457700-20190515.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457700-20190515.htm&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2PilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=a92d1219\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457700-20190515.htm&h=b46defb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457700-20190515.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2a109eecbe41226481e64fd44d25f9762b878cc1","tid":1156191,"uid":130695,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:36:08.000Z","msg":"喂 你班西環撚文員黎架<br />\n講閪咩"},{"pid":"acb73e19c0a47aee2f3c14dba5f4d5d8811543f5","tid":1156191,"uid":247117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:37:08.000Z","msg":"&quot;一制&quot;  港人治港  高度自治"},{"pid":"e7bd13157327edfdbd55a6a5b6dbe9215b27efc0","tid":1156191,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"acb73e19c0a47aee2f3c14dba5f4d5d8811543f5","tid":1156191,"uid":247117,"li